# thelakesvegas.com — core

- **Stack:** Next.js 15 App Router, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind. Alias `@/*` → `src/*`.
- **Validate:** After app changes, run `npm run lint`, `npm run type-check`, `npm run build` (matches [`.github/workflows/ci.yml`](.github/workflows/ci.yml)).
- **Secrets:** Never commit `.env` / `.env.local`. New vars → document placeholders in [`.env.example`](.env.example) only.
- **IDX/MLS:** Do not edit `src/components/idx/*` without explicit MLS/IDX approval.
- **RealScout:** Load **only** in [`src/app/layout.tsx`](src/app/layout.tsx) — `https://em.realscout.com/widgets/realscout-web-components.umd.js` (`afterInteractive`, single tag). Widget markup elsewhere uses `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`; do not add a second script tag. CSP in [`next.config.ts`](next.config.ts) must keep **`em.realscout.com`** and **`www.realscout.com`** in `script-src` and `connect-src`, plus **`fonts.googleapis.com`** / **`fonts.gstatic.com`** in `style-src` / `font-src` for the widget’s Google Fonts (mirror any duplicate header config).
- **Other third-party scripts in layout:** GA (`googletagmanager.com`), **Calendly** (`assets.calendly.com`). If you add domains, extend CSP consistently.
- **Host / deploy:** Canonical public host is **`www`** ([`src/middleware.ts`](src/middleware.ts) redirects apex → `www`). With **Cloudflare**, use **DNS only** (gray cloud) when fronting **Vercel** to avoid SSL/proxy issues.
- **SEO / NAP:** Visible NAP and JSON-LD ([`src/lib/site-config.ts`](src/lib/site-config.ts), [`src/lib/schema.ts`](src/lib/schema.ts)) must stay consistent with **Google Business Profile** when you change agent/office copy.
- **Copy / naming:** **Dr. Jan Duffy** (not “Janet”), BHHS Nevada Properties — license and phone live in `site-config`.
- **Scope:** Minimal diffs; match neighboring files. More detail: scoped rules under `.cursor/rules/` and [`AGENTS.md`](AGENTS.md).
